    Frequently asked questions

    What makes BAIE-TOTE bags unique?

    Our totes are expertly crafted with high-quality waterproof polyester and PU leather , enhanced with sophisticated embroidery . Each bag is designed with custom compartments to securely hold laptops, tablets, documents, and daily essentials – blending style, durability, and practicality for modern women.

    Can the tote fit my laptop?

    Yes! The independent padded laptop compartment fits laptops up to 15.6" or 17.3" , along with a 13" tablet . Protective padding ensures safe transport at all times.

    Are BAIE-TOTE bags waterproof?

    Our bags are made from waterproof polyester and PU fabric , making them resistant to splashes and light rain. They also feature anti-scratch, wear-resistant, and anti-wrinkle properties for long-lasting use.

    Is the bag comfortable to carry?

    Absolutely. Each tote comes with a detachable and adjustable shoulder strap , allowing you to customize the fit for maximum comfort, whether carried by hand, over the shoulder, or crossbody.

    How is the interior organized?

    The interior features:

    • Custom compartments for A4 documents, folders, laptops, and tablets.
    • A built-in key leash , dedicated water bottle pocket , and umbrella sleeve .
    • A multi-purpose pouch to organize tech accessories like chargers and cables.
    • This smart layout keeps every item neatly in place.
    What is the return policy?

    We accept returns on unused, unworn, and unwashed items within 30 days of delivery. You can choose a refund to your original payment method or store credit . Final sale items are not eligible.

    Non-Returnable Items:

    • Worn, washed, or damaged products
    • Items returned without original tags or packaging
    When will I get my order?

    We offer free shipping on all Orders. Regular shipping averages 3-5 business days (please allow 2 business days for order processing).
